{"tid":1384341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大欖車禍】近汀九橋兩巴士撞　司機被困最少78人傷　往九龍塞爆","createTime":"2019-07-30T01:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T01:59:34.000Z","uid":40152,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"28ef6d7b70c5d8c87e7d691cd0c7e53b1e36f626","tid":1384341,"uid":40152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:24:27.000Z","msg":"今日（30日）早上八時許，青朗公路近汀九橋往九龍方向，發生嚴重車禍，兩輛巴士相撞，巴士司機一度被困，事件中最少78人受傷。多輛救護車到場，消防員到場營救，將爆開後方巴士上層玻璃拯救。警方仍在調查意外原因。現場可見，肇事巴士撞至車頭擋風玻璃碎裂，車頭亦撞至變形。車禍大有大量傷者，他們坐在地面等待救援，救護員為傷者包紮分流。據了解，車禍中兩人危殆，10人嚴重及65人穩定。<br />\n<br />\n九巴乘客：有一個女人飛咗出嚟！<br />\n<br />\n前車九巴的鄧小姐乘客表示，當時她坐在巴士上層位置，其間她已入睡，突然後方的城巴猛撞九巴，「一下嘭，之後有好多濃煙！有一個女人（走廊）飛咗出嚟，有人連眼鏡都飛咗出嚟。」她指出，肇事的城巴乘客相對嚴重，事發時兩車相撞約三次。鄧小姐與同行的李小姐指，她們沒有大礙，只是背部及頸部撞傷，不過吸入大量濃煙。<br />\n<br />\n運輸處於早上8時49分宣佈，因較早前交通事故，屯門公路往九龍方向的交通繁忙。 現時在屯門公路往九龍方向的車龍龍尾已到元朗公路近唐人新村。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/357783/%E5%A4%A7%E6%AC%96%E9%9A%A7%E9%81%93%E8%BF%91%E6%B1%80%E4%B9%9D%E6%A9%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E6%92%9E-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E8%A2%AB%E5%9B%B0%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%9140%E4%BA%BA%E5%82%B7-%E5%BE%80%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%E5%A1%9E%E7%88%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F357783%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25AC%2596%25E9%259A%25A7%25E9%2581%2593%25E8%25BF%2591%25E6%25B1%2580%25E4%25B9%259D%25E6%25A9%258B%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%2592%259E-%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%259B%25B0%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25B0%259140%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2582%25B7-%25E5%25BE%2580%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%25A1%259E%25E7%2588%2586&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmtagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=7af61541\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/357783/%E5%A4%A7%E6%AC%96%E9%9A%A7%E9%81%93%E8%BF%91%E6%B1%80%E4%B9%9D%E6%A9%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E6%92%9E-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E8%A2%AB%E5%9B%B0%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%9140%E4%BA%BA%E5%82%B7-%E5%BE%80%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%E5%A1%9E%E7%88%86</a>"},{"pid":"79955cd6752955a7a9c19fa34931fbfc966f1e2d","tid":1384341,"uid":144001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:26:18.000Z","msg":"真不合作運動"},{"pid":"ebca41f541d1fb653c57db4bddb560963365ef6a","tid":1384341,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:31:15.000Z","msg":"希望司機乘客無事"},{"pid":"e63d03fa1e97f112341263bcb342772864248dcd","tid":1384341,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22b8ab84d3e0f617ad2fed267adb34a05acb427","tid":1384341,"uid":24345,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:33:15.000Z","msg":"真車禍，下面啲comments唔好講on9嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ababebcf55f8485e338a59afca59b7880472dc9","tid":1384341,"uid":139438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:44:17.000Z","msg":"希望人冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc4d0f80fecd0bde4530b1bbcf366c86ace2e70","tid":1384341,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:56:24.000Z","msg":"真車禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望冇事"},{"pid":"1fe74d58c03976e65f76352f4c08d0b7fb96cfca","tid":1384341,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:57:30.000Z","msg":"傷者早日康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8369aeb5d468957331c341d74a46d2043166bcd3","tid":1384341,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:59:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /